---
/** Ajustes de documento CV (visibilidad, impresión, formato); abre desde icono engrane en cabecera. */
---

<div
  data-cv-settings-modal
  class="fixed inset-0 z-[960] hidden flex-col items-stretch justify-center p-3 sm:p-5 print:hidden"
  role="dialog"
  aria-modal="true"
  aria-labelledby="cv-settings-modal-title"
>
  <div
    data-cv-settings-backdrop
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950/55 backdrop-blur-[2px] opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 motion-reduce:transition-none"
  ></div>
  <div
    data-cv-settings-panel
    class="relative z-10 mx-auto w-full min-w-0 max-w-[min(76rem,calc(100vw-1.5rem))] max-h-[min(92vh,56rem)] overflow-y-auto overflow-x-hidden rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 bg-white p-5 shadow-2xl dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-950 opacity-0 scale-95 translate-y-3 transition-all duration-300 ease-out motion-reduce:transition-none motion-reduce:translate-y-0"
  >
    <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 border-b border-gray-200/80 pb-3 dark:border-gray-800">
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <h2 id="cv-settings-modal-title" class="m-0 text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100" data-i18n="cv.settingsModalTitle">
          Ajustes del documento
        </h2>
        <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.settingsModalSubtitle">
          Visibilidad de secciones, PDF y formato de fechas.
        </p>
      </div>
      <button
        type="button"
        data-cv-settings-close
        class="shrink-0 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:border-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-900"
        data-i18n="common.close"
      >
        Cerrar
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4 min-w-0 space-y-5">
      <div class="min-w-0 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/80 dark:bg-gray-900/40 p-4">
        <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-i18n="cv.sectionVisibilityTitle">Visibilidad en el CV</p>
        <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-[11px] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.sectionVisibilityHint">
          Desmarca lo que no quieres mostrar en la vista previa ni al imprimir.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-sm">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-sec-show="highlights" checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.secHighlights">Logros</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-sec-show="projects" checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.secProjects">Proyectos</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-sec-show="experience" checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.secExperience">Experiencia</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-sec-show="education" checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.secEducation">Educación</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-sec-show="certifications" checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.secCertifications">Certificaciones</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-sec-show="languages" checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.secLanguages">Idiomas</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-sec-show="summary" checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.secSummary">Resumen / bio en el CV</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-sec-show="coverLetters" checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.secCoverLetters">Cartas de presentación</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="min-w-0 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/80 dark:bg-gray-900/40 p-4">
        <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-i18n="cv.printLayoutTitle">Impresión y PDF</p>
        <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-[11px] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.printLayoutHint">
          Si eliges 1 página, el PDF reduce tipografía con prioridad de cabecera; oculta secciones o acorta textos largos para que quepa sin perder legibilidad.
        </p>
        <label class="mt-3 block w-full min-w-0 max-w-md space-y-1">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-i18n="cv.printMaxPagesLabel">Máximo de páginas (objetivo)</span>
          <select
            data-cv-print-max-pages
            class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
          >
            <option value="1">1</option>
            <option value="2">2</option>
            <option value="3">3</option>
            <option value="4">4</option>
            <option value="5">5</option>
            <option value="6">6</option>
          </select>
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="min-w-0 rounded-xl border border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/80 dark:bg-gray-900/40 p-4">
        <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200" data-i18n="cv.formatPrefsTitle">Formato del contenido</p>
        <p class="m-0 mt-1 text-[11px] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.formatPrefsHint">
          Fechas, ubicaciones y nivel de detalle en experiencia, educación y proyectos.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <label class="space-y-1">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.dateExpLabel">Fechas · experiencia</span>
            <select
              data-cv-date-exp
              class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
            >
              <option value="full" data-i18n="cv.dateModeFull">Mes y año</option>
              <option value="year" data-i18n="cv.dateModeYear">Solo año</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="space-y-1">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cv.dateEduLabel">Fechas · educación</span>
            <select
              data-cv-date-edu
              class="w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
            >
              <option value="full" data-i18n="cv.dateModeFull">Mes y año</option>
              <option value="year" data-i18n="cv.dateModeYear">Solo año</option>
            </select>
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-show-contact-location checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.showContactLocation">Mostrar ubicación en contacto</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-show-exp-location checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.showExpLocation">Ubicación en experiencia</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-show-edu-location checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.showEduLocation">Ubicación en educación</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-show-edu-details checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.showEduDetails">Detalles / bullets en educación</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer sm:col-span-2">
            <input type="checkbox" data-cv-show-proj-desc checked class="rounded border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />
            <span data-i18n="cv.showProjDesc">Descripciones largas en proyectos</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
